            <h4>What is the current population of Sophia?</h4>
            <p>
                Based on the latest 2022 data from the US census, the
                current population of Sophia is 1,107.  Sophia, West Virginia is the 9,831st largest city in the US.
            </p>

            

            

            <h4>What was the peak population of Sophia?</h4>
            <p>
                
                    The peak population of Sophia was in
                    2010, when its population was
                    1,344.
                    
                        In 2010, Sophia was the
                        9,090th largest city in the US; now
                        its fallen to the 9,831st largest city in
                        the US.
                    
                    Sophia is currently
                        <span style="color: red;">
                            17.6%
                            smaller
                        </span>
                        than it was in 2010.
                    </p>
                
            </p>
            
                
                    <h4>How quickly is Sophia shrinking?</h4>
                
                <p>
                    
                        Sophia has shrunk
                        14.5% 
                        since the year 2000.
                    


                    
                        Sophia, West Virginia's growth is extremely below
                        average.
                        82% of similarly sized
                        cities are growing faster since 2000.
                    
                </p>
            

            

            

            

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
